  "title": "Maxema - Flow - Personalized and promotional pens. Promotional writing instruments and custom printed pens.",
  "description": "Flow Flow, Maxema’s latest creation, is the offshoot of research into materials and design. The svelte, aerodynamic clip is independent of the cap, thus permitting new colour contrasts. In the highly innovative and dynamic Texture version, the surface of the cap features a honeycomb design that creates visual and tactile elegance.",
